{"tid":2218154,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"解放軍造假｜東風-11十彈齊發咁威風？ 被揭剪接戈壁沙漠舊片","createTime":"2020-09-26T04:18:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T07:19:05.000Z","uid":56115,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"52528bc54be87ac459cac405ea29b8dfb021266b","tid":2218154,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T04:18:07.000Z","msg":"《解放軍報》昨日發佈的影片未說明時間、地點及發射飛彈型號，但官媒《環球時報》等多家媒體紛紛轉發，更有多款影片被加上字幕，聲稱片中發射的飛彈為「東風-11A飛彈」。鑑於東部戰區專責對台作戰，加上射程300至800公里的東風-11、東風-11A飛彈被視為中共對台作戰的主要武器，共軍喉舌釋出影片恫嚇意味濃厚。<br />\n<br />\n實際上，這已非共軍首度藉剪接造假軍演影片，對台展開文攻武嚇。「解放軍空軍政治工作部宣傳文化中心」周日曝光轟-6轟炸機模擬突襲疑似關島安德森空軍基地等畫面，被眼尖網友踢爆，影片畫面竟是非法剪接自《變形金剛2：復仇之戰》、《絕地任務》及《危機倒數》等3部荷李活電影。"},{"pid":"71be9478041c1396593f94c5473c863594e76bf2","tid":2218154,"uid":56115,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T04:18:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200926/XXDXMMM73VHRXLFDO43R4Q66LE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200926%2FXXDXMMM73VHRXLFDO43R4Q66LE%2F&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTu%2FzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=7bc20555\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200926%2FXXDXMMM73VHRXLFDO43R4Q66LE%2F&h=37460795\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200926/XXDXMMM73VHRXLFDO43R4Q66LE/</a>"},{"pid":"cb168b007c1d54a07373ecb6871ecdcde58976aa","tid":2218154,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T04:19:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84f0c4688bb680b86f6516ea9bf5750f6af14922","tid":2218154,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T04:22:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41800395083974a68ef058dcb8c9cc3599c59e38","tid":2218154,"uid":54125,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T04:23:47.000Z","msg":"